videos.description: Jalin Moore rushes in for a 2-yard score to give the Mountaineers an early lead.
videos.headline: Moore puts Appalachian State on the board first

videos.description: Levi Duffield extends the Appalachian State lead with 57 yard score.
videos.headline: Lamb finds Duffield wide open for a 57 yard score

videos.description: Taylor Lamb completes a 16-yard pass to  Zy Letman who takes it to the end zone to widen the Mountaineers lead.
videos.headline: Appalachian State extends lead with 16-yard TD

videos.description: Taylor Lamb connects with Collin Reed who is  wide open down field for a 68-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mountaineers score on another long TD pass

videos.description: Jalen Virgil catches a pass from Taylor Lamb and dodges multiple defenders on his way to the end zone.
videos.headline: Virgil pulls off impressive 56-yard catch and run for Appalachian State

videos.description: Collin Reed hauls in a 16-yard pass from Taylor Lamb and slides into the end zone in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Reed slides into the end zone for a Appalachian State TD
